Comment: 0,0:00:33.72,0:00:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,變化為巨人戰鬥
Comment: 0,0:00:38.53,0:00:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連被打倒
Comment: 0,0:00:40.28,0:00:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,並將艾連綁走
Comment: 0,0:00:48.44,0:00:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,把艾連
Comment: 0,0:00:50.53,0:00:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,還給我!
Comment: 0,0:01:03.56,0:01:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不管在哪裡
Comment: 0,0:01:05.23,0:01:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我都要殺了那女人
Comment: 0,0:01:07.24,0:01:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,把她的身體剖開
Comment: 0,0:01:09.46,0:01:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,從那骯髒的地方把你拖出來
Comment: 0,0:01:13.88,0:01:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,對不起 艾連
Comment: 0,0:01:16.08,0:01:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,再給我...
Comment: 0,0:01:18.35,0:01:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,一點時間...
Comment: 0,0:01:27.01,0:01:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,站住!
Comment: 0,0:01:29.16,0:01:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,什麼?!
Comment: 0,0:01:32.34,0:01:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,暫時先離她遠一點
Comment: 0,0:01:33.36,0:01:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,OP
Comment: 0,0:03:19.07,0:03:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,保持這樣的距離
Comment: 0,0:03:21.42,0:03:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,她應該也累了吧
Comment: 0,0:03:22.97,0:03:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,速度不像之前那麼快了
Comment: 0,0:03:25.96,0:03:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連好像被連著後頸一起咬下來了
Comment: 0,0:03:28.84,0:03:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連死了嗎?
Comment: 0,0:03:33.43,0:03:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,還活著
Comment: 0,0:03:35.03,0:03:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那傢伙應該具有智慧
Comment: 0,0:03:37.35,0:03:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,她的目的是帶走艾連
Comment: 0,0:03:40.51,0:03:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,如果想殺他的話早就會動手了
Comment: 0,0:03:43.99,0:03:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那傢伙卻刻意將他含在嘴裡一邊戰鬥一邊逃走
Comment: 0,0:03:49.37,0:03:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,她的目的也可能是要吃了艾連
Comment: 0,0:03:51.97,0:03:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這麼一來
Comment: 0,0:03:52.86,0:03:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連應該早就被吞下肚了
Comment: 0,0:03:54.73,0:03:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,照常理來說應該早就掛了
Comment: 0,0:03:56.91,0:03:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,他還活著!
Comment: 0,0:04:00.56,0:04:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是的話就好了...
Comment: 0,0:04:03.76,0:04:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,況且
Comment: 0,0:04:05.11,0:04:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,如果你能夠保護好艾連
Comment: 0,0:04:06.92,0:04:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就不會導致這種事情發生了
Comment: 0,0:04:12.12,0:04:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是這樣嗎...
Comment: 0,0:04:13.40,0:04:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你就是當時...
Comment: 0,0:04:15.76,0:04:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連的好朋友嗎?
Comment: 0,0:04:20.11,0:04:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那我們目標縮小為一個
Comment: 0,0:04:22.75,0:04:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,首先
Comment: 0,0:04:23.76,0:04:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,放棄將女巨人殺掉
Comment: 0,0:04:25.79,0:04:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那傢伙...
Comment: 0,0:04:26.85,0:04:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,殺了很多我們的同伴啊
Comment: 0,0:04:29.54,0:04:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,只要她具有皮膚硬化能力那就不可能殺了她
Comment: 0,0:04:32.97,0:04:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,聽從我的判斷吧
Comment: 0,0:04:35.19,0:04:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,將一切的希望都賭在艾連還活著的前提上
Comment: 0,0:04:38.68,0:04:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,並在她離開森林之前把他救出來
Comment: 0,0:04:41.36,0:04:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我負責砍她
Comment: 0,0:04:42.92,0:04:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,妳去吸引她的注意力
Comment: 0,0:05:44.19,0:05:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,太快了!
Comment: 0,0:05:45.15,0:05:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,快到她根本無法以硬化來抵擋攻擊
Comment: 0,0:06:01.23,0:06:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,她的後頸...
Comment: 0,0:06:02.41,0:06:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,有機會!
Comment: 0,0:06:03.93,0:06:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,她已經累了
Comment: 0,0:06:05.06,0:06:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,現在一定動不了
Comment: 0,0:06:07.11,0:06:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我能殺了她!
Comment: 0,0:06:11.72,0:06:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,住手!
Comment: 0,0:06:27.60,0:06:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連!
Comment: 0,0:06:35.60,0:06:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,喂!
Comment: 0,0:06:37.76,0:06:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我們要離開了!!
Comment: 0,0:06:39.21,0:06:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連
Comment: 0,0:06:42.07,0:06:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,他應該沒事 還活著
Comment: 0,0:06:44.56,0:06:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,雖然蠻髒的
Comment: 0,0:06:46.45,0:06:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不要理她了
Comment: 0,0:06:48.36,0:06:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我們快撤退!
Comment: 0,0:06:50.88,0:06:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,別忘了作戰的本質
Comment: 0,0:06:53.98,0:06:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,滿足自己的慾望比較重要嗎?
Comment: 0,0:06:57.62,0:06:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,他是妳重視的朋友對吧?
Comment: 0,0:07:02.81,0:07:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不...
Comment: 0,0:07:04.20,0:07:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我是...
Comment: 0,0:07:23.28,0:07:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,已經回來了嗎?
Comment: 0,0:07:26.19,0:07:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,發生了什麼事?
Comment: 0,0:07:27.72,0:07:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,啊災
Comment: 0,0:07:29.41,0:07:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,反正一定是拖著一堆死人回來吧
Comment: 0,0:07:49.04,0:07:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾魯多好像快回來了喔
Comment: 0,0:07:55.75,0:07:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是嗎...
Comment: 0,0:07:59.33,0:08:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,歐魯他不知道有沒有空回家裡一趟啊
Comment: 0,0:08:03.49,0:08:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,反正多做一份放著又不會怎樣
Comment: 0,0:08:11.11,0:08:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,君達要回來囉
Comment: 0,0:08:17.52,0:08:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這樣啊...
Comment: 0,0:09:19.99,0:09:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這種工作還真無法習慣啊
Comment: 0,0:09:23.41,0:09:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,誰都是這樣的啦
Comment: 0,0:09:26.52,0:09:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,夥伴是怎麼死的
