Comment: 0,0:11:03.20,0:11:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,喂! 我說你...
Comment: 0,0:11:05.21,0:11:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我們應該去回收才對!
Comment: 0,0:11:06.88,0:11:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,伊凡的屍體明明就在眼前而已!
Comment: 0,0:11:09.95,0:11:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我不是說了巨人就在旁邊嗎?!
Comment: 0,0:11:12.44,0:11:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,有可能造成二次傷害
Comment: 0,0:11:14.49,0:11:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,衝過來的話幹掉他不就好了嗎!
Comment: 0,0:11:18.01,0:11:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,伊凡他是我從小就認識的同鄉啊!
Comment: 0,0:11:20.78,0:11:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,他的父母我也認識
Comment: 0,0:11:22.67,0:11:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我想至少也要把他給帶回去
Comment: 0,0:11:24.98,0:11:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不要任性了!
Comment: 0,0:11:26.22,0:11:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,小屁孩的吵架嗎?
Comment: 0,0:11:28.65,0:11:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,里維士官長...
Comment: 0,0:11:30.49,0:11:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,如果已經確認是死亡的話
Comment: 0,0:11:32.23,0:11:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這樣就夠了吧
Comment: 0,0:11:34.19,0:11:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,無論有沒有屍體 死亡就是死亡
Comment: 0,0:11:37.56,0:11:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這點並不會有改變
Comment: 0,0:11:40.17,0:11:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,怎麼這樣...
Comment: 0,0:11:42.15,0:11:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,伊凡他們將以失蹤處理
Comment: 0,0:11:44.97,0:11:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這已經是既定事項
Comment: 0,0:11:46.43,0:11:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,放棄吧
Comment: 0,0:11:50.74,0:11:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你們兩個...
Comment: 0,0:11:52.46,0:11:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,難道就沒有一點人性嗎?!
Comment: 0,0:11:55.98,0:11:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,喂! 迪塔爾!
Comment: 0,0:11:57.28,0:11:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你說過頭了啦!
Comment: 0,0:11:58.45,0:12:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,CM
Comment: 0,0:12:43.67,0:12:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是巨人!!
Comment: 0,0:12:52.49,0:12:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那個是...
Comment: 0,0:12:55.46,0:12:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,迪塔爾!
Comment: 0,0:13:00.55,0:13:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那個白癡...
Comment: 0,0:13:05.18,0:13:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,後方列隊發現巨人!!
Comment: 0,0:13:07.96,0:13:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,全速前進!
Comment: 0,0:13:09.75,0:13:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒有看到巨大的樹木
Comment: 0,0:13:11.52,0:13:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,也沒看到建築物
Comment: 0,0:13:13.59,0:13:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,看來沒有辦法進行戰鬥啊...
Comment: 0,0:13:15.98,0:13:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,往城牆移動還比較快
Comment: 0,0:13:44.75,0:13:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這樣下去會被追上的!
Comment: 0,0:13:46.79,0:13:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,難道只能戰鬥了嗎?
Comment: 0,0:13:49.09,0:13:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,在曠野中展開立體機動會有它的極限
Comment: 0,0:13:52.00,0:13:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,所以你看... 根本沒完沒了
Comment: 0,0:13:56.03,0:13:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那麼... 到底該怎麼辦啦!
Comment: 0,0:14:01.30,0:14:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這個...
Comment: 0,0:14:38.52,0:14:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不行了! 會被追上!!
Comment: 0,0:14:40.36,0:14:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我來繞到他背後
Comment: 0,0:14:41.95,0:14:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,總之先削了他的肉你再趁機...
Comment: 0,0:14:43.49,0:14:44.49,Upside,,0,0,0,karaoke,住手
Comment: 0,0:14:45.26,0:14:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,先把屍體給扔了
Comment: 0,0:14:47.28,0:14:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,再這樣會被追上的
Comment: 0,0:14:48.84,0:14:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但...但是...
Comment: 0,0:14:50.62,0:14:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,回不去的屍體少說也已經有五萬個了
Comment: 0,0:14:54.63,0:14:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這些人並非什麼特殊人物
Comment: 0,0:14:58.22,0:14:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,要這樣做嗎?
Comment: 0,0:15:00.19,0:15:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,真的要這樣做嗎?
Comment: 0,0:15:06.32,0:15:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,可惡!
Comment: 0,0:15:10.03,0:15:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,也只能這麼做了!
Comment: 0,0:15:41.04,0:15:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,很好!
Comment: 0,0:15:42.66,0:15:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就這樣子前進下去!
Comment: 0,0:15:56.36,0:15:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,確認好所在位置後
Comment: 0,0:15:57.77,0:15:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就立刻啟程!
Comment: 0,0:15:59.31,0:16:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,警戒不要鬆懈了!
Comment: 0,0:16:01.11,0:16:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,需要稍微往東方修正路線
Comment: 0,0:16:12.26,0:16:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,里維士官長...
Comment: 0,0:16:14.79,0:16:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我啊...
Comment: 0,0:16:19.53,0:16:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這就是那些人活過的證明
Comment: 0,0:16:23.28,0:16:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,對我來說啦
Comment: 0,0:16:29.51,0:16:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這是伊凡的
Comment: 0,0:16:36.86,0:16:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,士官長...
Comment: 0,0:16:55.14,0:16:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,出發了!
Comment: 0,0:17:16.07,0:17:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連
Comment: 0,0:17:17.29,0:17:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我勸你還是別加入調查軍團吧
Comment: 0,0:17:20.26,0:17:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,什麼啊...
Comment: 0,0:17:21.25,0:17:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,難道妳也瞧不起調查軍團嗎?
Comment: 0,0:17:23.85,0:17:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,並不是瞧不瞧得起的問題...
Comment: 0,0:17:33.27,0:17:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,調查軍團回來了!
Comment: 0,0:17:35.76,0:17:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,大門要開了哦!!
Comment: 0,0:17:37.49,0:17:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,走吧! 米卡莎
Comment: 0,0:17:38.55,0:17:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,英雄凱旋歸來了!
Comment: 0,0:17:59.51,0:18:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,只有這些人回來啊...
Comment: 0,0:18:02.60,0:18:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,大家都被吃掉了吧?
Comment: 0,0:18:05.32,0:18:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,自己愛亂跑出去才會變成這樣
Comment: 0,0:18:08.89,0:18:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這樣豈不是用我們繳的稅來買飼料養肥他們嗎?
Comment: 0,0:18:14.01,0:18:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連
Comment: 0,0:18:19.73,0:18:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,怎麼了?
Comment: 0,0:18:29.66,0:18:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連...
Comment: 0,0:18:36.46,0:18:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連!
Comment: 0,0:18:46.51,0:18:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連...
Comment: 0,0:18:54.03,0:18:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你還不能起來
Comment: 0,0:18:56.68,0:18:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,要好好休息
Comment: 0,0:18:59.30,0:19:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,女巨人呢?
Comment: 0,0:19:01.81,0:19:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,被她跑了
Comment: 0,0:19:03.88,0:19:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為什麼...
Comment: 0,0:19:05.57,0:19:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,大家...
Comment: 0,0:19:06.78,0:19:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,到底...
Comment: 0,0:19:08.97,0:19:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,作戰呢?
Comment: 0,0:19:11.26,0:19:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,失敗了...
Comment: 0,0:19:13.29,0:19:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,現在先休息吧
Comment: 0,0:19:17.50,0:19:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這是...
Comment: 0,0:19:19.82,0:19:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,難道又是妳救了我?
Comment: 0,0:19:26.75,0:19:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就快要... 抵達城牆了
Comment: 0,0:19:47.48,0:19:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,人數好像比今天早上還要少很多啊...
Comment: 0,0:19:51.49,0:19:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,變少了許多呢
Comment: 0,0:19:53.72,0:19:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這次也很慘啊...
Comment: 0,0:19:57.05,0:20:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,早上還大張旗鼓地出發 結果現在就回來啦
Comment: 0,0:20:01.23,0:20:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,到底是去幹嘛的?
Comment: 0,0:20:03.41,0:20:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,誰知道咧
Comment: 0,0:20:05.31,0:20:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不過看他們表情這麼凝重
Comment: 0,0:20:09.88,0:20:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,大概又成功地浪費了我們的納稅錢啦
Comment: 0,0:20:16.89,0:20:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連
Comment: 0,0:20:18.02,0:20:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,忍耐一點
Comment: 0,0:20:30.02,0:20:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,好帥!
Comment: 0,0:20:31.56,0:20:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,調查軍團超強的!!
Comment: 0,0:20:34.13,0:20:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就算遍體鱗傷也還是堅持要戰鬥下去!
Comment: 0,0:20:57.79,0:20:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,士官長大哥!
Comment: 0,0:20:59.78,0:21:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,女兒平時多虧您照顧了!
Comment: 0,0:21:01.95,0:21:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我是佩托拉的父親
Comment: 0,0:21:03.77,0:21:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,在見到女兒前有些話想跟您說
Comment: 0,0:21:07.33,0:21:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,女兒寄了封信給我啊
Comment: 0,0:21:10.33,0:21:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,她說自己的本事被看上
Comment: 0,0:21:11.43,0:21:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,被調到您底下做事
Comment: 0,0:21:14.14,0:21:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,還說願意為您獻出自己的一切
Comment: 0,0:21:17.22,0:21:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,真是的... 都不顧父母的擔心
Comment: 0,0:21:19.83,0:21:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,竟然已經開始談情說愛了!
Comment: 0,0:21:23.65,0:21:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這個啊...
Comment: 0,0:21:24.86,0:21:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,唉...
Comment: 0,0:21:25.64,0:21:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我這個做父親的啊
Comment: 0,0:21:27.69,0:21:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我覺得讓她嫁出去可能還太早了
Comment: 0,0:21:31.15,0:21:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,況且她還年輕...
Comment: 0,0:21:32.68,0:21:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,接下來還有很多...
Comment: 0,0:21:35.13,0:21:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾爾文團長!
Comment: 0,0:21:36.51,0:21:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,請你回答!
Comment: 0,0:21:38.10,0:21:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這次遠征的收獲能夠彌補掉這次的犧牲嗎?
Comment: 0,0:21:42.23,0:21:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你覺得自己對得起那些死去的士兵嗎?
Comment: 0,0:21:48.92,0:21:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這次牆外遠征所消耗的費用跟造成的損害
Comment: 0,0:21:53.86,0:21:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,已經足以打垮原本支持調查軍團的力量了
Comment: 0,0:22:08.08,0:22:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,包含艾爾文團長在內的負責人
Comment: 0,0:22:10.42,0:22:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,都被傳喚至王都的同時
Comment: 0,0:22:14.19,0:22:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,也決定將艾連引渡回去...
Comment: 0,0:22:16.16,0:22:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,ED
Comment: 0,0:23:53.29,0:23:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那一天亞妮
Comment: 0,0:23:54.70,0:23:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,負責被王都召喚的艾連的護送警衛
Comment: 0,0:23:59.18,0:24:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,並從突然現身的阿爾敏
Comment: 0,0:24:02.33,0:24:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,得知她被選入了某項機密作戰計畫...
