Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.95,0:03:14.95,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs35\fsp5\bord2\blur5\c&HCDCDCD&\pos(961,750)}─第五十七次牆外調查⑥─
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.97,0:24:06.97,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\fsp5\bord2\blur5\c&HCDCDCD&\pos(961,700)}微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.97,0:24:06.97,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs35\fsp5\bord2\blur5\c&HCDCDCD&\pos(961,750)}─史托黑斯區突襲①─
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.89,0:00:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}果然...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.96,0:00:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}要來了!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.25,0:00:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是女巨人!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.75,0:00:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}因為復活的女巨人的出現
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.46,0:00:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}里維班的精英們一個接著一個地倒下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.62,0:00:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}殺了妳!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.82,0:00:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}認為夥伴被殺死是自己的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.51,0:00:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}並下定決心要報仇的艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.72,0:00:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}變化為巨人戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.53,0:00:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連被打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.28,0:00:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}並將艾連綁走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.44,0:00:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}把艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.53,0:00:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}還給我!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.56,0:01:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不管在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.23,0:01:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我都要殺了那女人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.24,0:01:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}把她的身體剖開
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.46,0:01:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}從那骯髒的地方把你拖出來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.88,0:01:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}對不起 艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.08,0:01:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}再給我...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.35,0:01:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}一點時間...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.01,0:01:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}站住!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.16,0:01:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}什麼?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.34,0:01:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}暫時先離她遠一點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.07,0:03:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}保持這樣的距離
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.42,0:03:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}她應該也累了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.97,0:03:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}速度不像之前那麼快了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.96,0:03:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連好像被連著後頸一起咬下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.84,0:03:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連死了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.43,0:03:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.03,0:03:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那傢伙應該具有智慧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.35,0:03:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}她的目的是帶走艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.51,0:03:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如果想殺他的話早就會動手了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.99,0:03:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那傢伙卻刻意將他含在嘴裡一邊戰鬥一邊逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.37,0:03:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}她的目的也可能是要吃了艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.97,0:03:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這麼一來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.86,0:03:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連應該早就被吞下肚了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.73,0:03:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}照常理來說應該早就掛了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.91,0:03:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}他還活著!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.56,0:04:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是的話就好了...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.76,0:04:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}況且
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.11,0:04:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如果你能夠保護好艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.92,0:04:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就不會導致這種事情發生了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.12,0:04:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是這樣嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.40,0:04:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你就是當時...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.76,0:04:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連的好朋友嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.11,0:04:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那我們目標縮小為一個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.75,0:04:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}首先
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.76,0:04:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}放棄將女巨人殺掉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.79,0:04:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那傢伙...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.85,0:04:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}殺了很多我們的同伴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.54,0:04:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}只要她具有皮膚硬化能力那就不可能殺了她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.97,0:04:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}聽從我的判斷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.19,0:04:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}將一切的希望都賭在艾連還活著的前提上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.68,0:04:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}並在她離開森林之前把他救出來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.36,0:04:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我負責砍她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.92,0:04:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}妳去吸引她的注意力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.19,0:05:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}太快了!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.15,0:05:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}快到她根本無法以硬化來抵擋攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.23,0:06:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}她的後頸...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.41,0:06:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}有機會!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.93,0:06:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}她已經累了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.06,0:06:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}現在一定動不了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.11,0:06:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我能殺了她!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.72,0:06:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}住手!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.60,0:06:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.60,0:06:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喂!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.76,0:06:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我們要離開了!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.21,0:06:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.07,0:06:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}他應該沒事 還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.56,0:06:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}雖然蠻髒的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.45,0:06:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不要理她了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.36,0:06:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我們快撤退!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.88,0:06:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}別忘了作戰的本質
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.98,0:06:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}滿足自己的慾望比較重要嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.62,0:06:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}他是妳重視的朋友對吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.81,0:07:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.20,0:07:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我是...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.28,0:07:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}已經回來了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.19,0:07:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}發生了什麼事?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.72,0:07:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}啊災
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.41,0:07:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}反正一定是拖著一堆死人回來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.04,0:07:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾魯多好像快回來了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.75,0:07:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.33,0:08:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}歐魯他不知道有沒有空回家裡一趟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.49,0:08:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}反正多做一份放著又不會怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.11,0:08:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}君達要回來囉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.52,0:08:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這樣啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.99,0:09:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這種工作還真無法習慣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.41,0:09:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}誰都是這樣的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.52,0:09:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}夥伴是怎麼死的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.86,0:09:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}自己又會是怎麼死的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.65,0:09:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我總會一直去想這些事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.32,0:09:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我總是讓自己不去想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.99,0:09:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如果去想像自己最後的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.89,0:09:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我想我大概會變得無法戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.49,0:09:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.87,0:09:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你說的沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.68,0:09:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我們能活到什麼時候啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.94,0:10:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}總之這次我們不是存活下來了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.75,0:10:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是「總之」啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.78,0:10:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這不是很好嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.94,0:10:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}畢竟我們還活著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.71,0:10:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}面對著戰友的屍體妳還說得出這種話嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.40,0:10:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}說不定我們已經回不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.63,0:10:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}基本上都完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.33,0:10:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}雖然有5具大體是無法回收的...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.93,0:10:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}一部分也不行嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.86,0:10:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}除了因為被巨人吃掉而無法回收以外的....
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.26,0:10:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如果有的話也不要帶回去 這樣對家屬也比較好...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.51,0:10:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那就當做是失蹤處理掉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.20,0:10:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.27,0:10:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}在森林的周邊發現了幾隻巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.25,0:10:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不過他們還沒開始向這裡移動
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.25,0:10:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}立刻從這裡撤出
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.00,0:10:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}幫我傳達給各班
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.53,0:10:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.51,0:11:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我不能認同! 艾爾文團長!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.20,0:11:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喂! 我說你...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.21,0:11:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我們應該去回收才對!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.88,0:11:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}伊凡的屍體明明就在眼前而已!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.95,0:11:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我不是說了巨人就在旁邊嗎?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.44,0:11:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}有可能造成二次傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.49,0:11:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}衝過來的話幹掉他不就好了嗎!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.01,0:11:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}伊凡他是我從小就認識的同鄉啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.78,0:11:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}他的父母我也認識
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.67,0:11:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我想至少也要把他給帶回去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.98,0:11:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不要任性了!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.22,0:11:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}小屁孩的吵架嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.65,0:11:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}里維士官長...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.49,0:11:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如果已經確認是死亡的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.23,0:11:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這樣就夠了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.19,0:11:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}無論有沒有屍體 死亡就是死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.56,0:11:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這點並不會有改變
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.17,0:11:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}怎麼這樣...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.15,0:11:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}伊凡他們將以失蹤處理
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.97,0:11:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這已經是既定事項
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.43,0:11:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}放棄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.74,0:11:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你們兩個...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.46,0:11:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}難道就沒有一點人性嗎?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.98,0:11:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喂! 迪塔爾!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.28,0:11:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你說過頭了啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.67,0:12:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是巨人!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.49,0:12:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那個是...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.46,0:12:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}迪塔爾!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.55,0:13:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那個白癡...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.18,0:13:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}後方列隊發現巨人!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.96,0:13:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}全速前進!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.75,0:13:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒有看到巨大的樹木
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.52,0:13:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}也沒看到建築物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.59,0:13:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}看來沒有辦法進行戰鬥啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.98,0:13:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}往城牆移動還比較快
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.75,0:13:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這樣下去會被追上的!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.79,0:13:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}難道只能戰鬥了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.09,0:13:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}在曠野中展開立體機動會有它的極限
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.00,0:13:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}所以你看... 根本沒完沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.03,0:13:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那麼... 到底該怎麼辦啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.30,0:14:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這個...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.52,0:14:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不行了! 會被追上!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.36,0:14:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我來繞到他背後
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.95,0:14:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}總之先削了他的肉你再趁機...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.49,0:14:44.49,Upside,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}住手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.26,0:14:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}先把屍體給扔了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.28,0:14:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}再這樣會被追上的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.84,0:14:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但...但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.62,0:14:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}回不去的屍體少說也已經有五萬個了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.63,0:14:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這些人並非什麼特殊人物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.22,0:14:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}要這樣做嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.19,0:15:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}真的要這樣做嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.32,0:15:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}可惡!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.03,0:15:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}也只能這麼做了!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.04,0:15:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}很好!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.66,0:15:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就這樣子前進下去!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.36,0:15:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}確認好所在位置後
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.77,0:15:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就立刻啟程!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.31,0:16:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}警戒不要鬆懈了!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.11,0:16:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}需要稍微往東方修正路線
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.26,0:16:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}里維士官長...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.79,0:16:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.53,0:16:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這就是那些人活過的證明
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.28,0:16:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}對我來說啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.51,0:16:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這是伊凡的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.86,0:16:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}士官長...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.14,0:16:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}出發了!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.07,0:17:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.29,0:17:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我勸你還是別加入調查軍團吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.26,0:17:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}什麼啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.25,0:17:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}難道妳也瞧不起調查軍團嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.85,0:17:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}並不是瞧不瞧得起的問題...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.27,0:17:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}調查軍團回來了!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.76,0:17:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}大門要開了哦!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.49,0:17:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}走吧! 米卡莎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.55,0:17:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}英雄凱旋歸來了!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.51,0:18:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}只有這些人回來啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.60,0:18:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}大家都被吃掉了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.32,0:18:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}自己愛亂跑出去才會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.89,0:18:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這樣豈不是用我們繳的稅來買飼料養肥他們嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.01,0:18:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.73,0:18:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.66,0:18:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.46,0:18:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.51,0:18:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.03,0:18:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你還不能起來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.68,0:18:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}要好好休息
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.30,0:19:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}女巨人呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.81,0:19:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}被她跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.88,0:19:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.57,0:19:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}大家...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.78,0:19:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}到底...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.97,0:19:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}作戰呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.26,0:19:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}失敗了...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.29,0:19:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}現在先休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.50,0:19:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這是...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.82,0:19:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}難道又是妳救了我?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.75,0:19:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就快要... 抵達城牆了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.48,0:19:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}人數好像比今天早上還要少很多啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.49,0:19:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}變少了許多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.72,0:19:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這次也很慘啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.05,0:20:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}早上還大張旗鼓地出發 結果現在就回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.23,0:20:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}到底是去幹嘛的?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.41,0:20:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}誰知道咧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.31,0:20:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不過看他們表情這麼凝重
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.88,0:20:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}大概又成功地浪費了我們的納稅錢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.89,0:20:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.02,0:20:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}忍耐一點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.02,0:20:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}好帥!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.56,0:20:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}調查軍團超強的!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.13,0:20:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就算遍體鱗傷也還是堅持要戰鬥下去!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.79,0:20:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}士官長大哥!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.78,0:21:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}女兒平時多虧您照顧了!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.95,0:21:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我是佩托拉的父親
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.77,0:21:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}在見到女兒前有些話想跟您說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.33,0:21:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}女兒寄了封信給我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.33,0:21:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}她說自己的本事被看上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.43,0:21:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}被調到您底下做事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.14,0:21:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}還說願意為您獻出自己的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.22,0:21:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}真是的... 都不顧父母的擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.83,0:21:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}竟然已經開始談情說愛了!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.65,0:21:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這個啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.86,0:21:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}唉...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.64,0:21:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我這個做父親的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.69,0:21:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我覺得讓她嫁出去可能還太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.15,0:21:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}況且她還年輕...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.68,0:21:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}接下來還有很多...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.13,0:21:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾爾文團長!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.51,0:21:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}請你回答!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.10,0:21:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這次遠征的收獲能夠彌補掉這次的犧牲嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.23,0:21:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你覺得自己對得起那些死去的士兵嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.92,0:21:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這次牆外遠征所消耗的費用跟造成的損害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.86,0:21:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}已經足以打垮原本支持調查軍團的力量了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.08,0:22:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}包含艾爾文團長在內的負責人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.42,0:22:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}都被傳喚至王都的同時
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.19,0:22:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}也決定將艾連引渡回去...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.29,0:23:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那一天亞妮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.70,0:23:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}負責被王都召喚的艾連的護送警衛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.18,0:24:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}並從突然現身的阿爾敏
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.33,0:24:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}得知她被選入了某項機密作戰計畫...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.45,0:12:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}
